  "original_title": "\u0b93\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba9 \u0b9a\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Dismissal of case against homosexual",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A case filed against a gay (lesbian) resident of Velisara-Mahabage area was dismissed by the Wattala Magistrate's Court.",
        "The case was dismissed after the court accepted the defense counsel's submission that homosexuality was neither a mental illness nor a crime.",
        "A case was filed against a 22-year-old gay woman in the Wattala Magistrate's Court. The victim's parents filed a petition in the court with the help of Velisara Mahabage police.",
        "They filed a petition demanding that she be declared mentally challenged because she is a lesbian.",
        "It was also brought to the notice of the court that the victim's parents illegally confined the adult girl and subjected her to abuse, torture and forced conversion services."
      ],
